      "settings": {
        "hd": "Welcome to the world of EVAMATS!",
        "des1": "<p>Hi, I'm Maks, and I create top-quality car floor mats designed with your comfort — and you — in mind!<br\/>Our company was born out of a passion for automotive excellence and a desire to give you the best possible driving experience.<\/p><p><strong>EVAMATS<\/strong> is not just about car mats. It's about innovative solutions that combine style, durability, and eco-friendly materials.<br\/>Our material is environmentally friendly, meaning you’re taking care of both your car and the planet.<\/p><p>Each of our sets is handcrafted from start to finish — like no other — ensuring exceptional quality and a perfect fit for every vehicle and every need.<\/p>",
        "img": "shopify:\/\/shop_images\/photo_2025-05-14_14.04.33.jpg",
        "des2": "<p><strong>EVAMATS material<\/strong> is an innovative, high-quality product that delivers durability, comfort, and great aesthetics.<br\/>Our mats are waterproof, maintain their shape, resistant to wear, and easy to clean.<br\/>We offer a product that outperforms standard rubber and velour mats in every way.<\/p><p><strong>Investing in our mats means investing for years to come!<\/strong><br\/>Over 50,000 satisfied drivers have already trusted us — and now it's your turn to discover why EVAMATS is the choice for those who value quality and comfort.<\/p><p>If you have any questions or need assistance, our team is here to help you.<\/p><p><strong>Experience a new level of comfort and enjoy your journeys in style with EVAMATS!<\/strong><\/p>"
      }
    },
